text: Castine-en-Plaine is a commune. It is found in the Normandy region in the Calvados department in northwestern France. The municipality was created on 1 January 2019 and consists of the former communes of Rocquancourt (the seat), Hubert-Folie and Tilly-la-Campagne.Arrêté préfectoral 19 December 2018, p. 10 == References == Category:2019 establishments in France Category:Communes in Calvados
title: Castine-en-Plaine
